data.description: Move in ready! Beautifully remodeled home including NEW roof, NEW HVAC system, 4+ bedroom, 3 bath, and woodland access. Step inside to an open floor plan that includes a main floor extra room that is wheelchair accessible with its own entrance and ramp, heated floor tile shower and bidet. The main floor offers a very large open floor-plan with large great room, custom entertainment center around the gas fireplace, spacious kitchen that includes a desk area, pantry, large island for family and friends, all new surfaces and appliances. Upstairs has 4 bedrooms including the master bedroom and bath. There is also a third bathroom in the upstairs hallway, and upstairs laundry room for your convenience. Step out back and enjoy a low maintenance yard with a section of artificial turf for multiple purposes, covered deck and seating area, open air BBQ patio, and new wood fence. Property offers gated access to the woodlands and a garden shed.
